title: MLS Futbolito! Logo
content:
I stumbled upon this little doozy of a script logo for a 4 on 4 soccer/football tournament.

Associated with: [http://www.mlsfutbolito.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20130819220526/http:/www.mlsfutbolito.com/)

The colors and the bitmappiness make it feel like a logo for a video game from the early `90s... or maybe some fast food startup.
